This paper is likely to belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category as it deals with rating prediction in recommendation systems using text reviews. It also involves natural language processing techniques such as attention mechanisms and latent factor models, which are commonly used in the Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) sub-category. Additionally, the use of machine learning algorithms for prediction makes it relevant to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper may also be relevant to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it involves the analysis of textual data.
